data.description: **Charming 3-Bed, 2-Bath Home on Half-Acre Lot**  This delightful 3-bed, 2-bath home offers space and comfort, with all new LVP flooring! Inside, find a modern kitchen and inviting living area with vaulted ceilings and a beautiful wood burning fireplace. The primary suite is isolated from the other bedrooms, for extra privacy. This home also boasts an expansive fenced backyard. Convenient location near schools, shopping, and under 20 minutes to the arsenal. With over half an acre, you have endless possibilities. Creek nearby for exploring!
